    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Texts having to do with devils, devil-lore, or the description or representation of devils. The term may refer to any representations in words or pictures of black magic or of dealings with the devil. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
